</svg>

</div>
</div>
</div>



<h2>
  <a name="conclusion" href="#conclusion">
  </a>
  Conclusion
</h2>

<p>We understood how to control nginx and how to configure nginx.</p>

<p>So, this makes solid foundation for us to understand how work with nginx.</p>

